**Retro #10 Summary — OpenWok: 7.6/10**

**Top 3 Findings:**
1. **Ghost runs are the #1 waste source** — 2 abandoned sessions (112 min) with zero output recovery. Real-time log streaming (`tee`) recommended for 4th consecutive retro.
